Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.78,1:28:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这点本事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.18,1:28:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没别的了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.89,1:28:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我只能杀掉你了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.59,1:28:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}武器重新装备
