Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.05,1:29:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.56,1:29:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.09,1:29:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.69,1:30:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我创造了你
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.74,1:30:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.03,1:30:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个大错
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.95,1:30:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莱尔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.01,1:30:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  趁还有时间
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.59,1:30:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走  我跟你后面
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.38,1:30:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}生命体征  危险
