Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.72,1:32:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是本体  他不是我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.28,1:34:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做到了  爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.48,1:34:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.88,1:34:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成功了
